- always use radix-ui components
- always use radix-ui theme and colors system
- always use radix-ui icons
- for any other additional styaling , plese use styled components
- when creating a component the name of the component always start with big letter and .tsx format; for example Header.ts
- when creating a styled component, it will have the same component name following by .style.ts - for example : Header.styles.ts